high_descs: Turn to the left and go the the small brown table on your right.
Pick up the knife laying next to the tomato.
Slice the tomato laying on the brown table.
Turn towards the fridge and back towards the brown table.
Lay the knife on the coffee maker.
Turn left towards the white table and then back towards the brown table.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn around and go across the room to the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the frying pan on the stove.
Pick up the frying pan with the tomato in it.
Turn around and head to the fridge across the room.
Put the frying pay in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a fried tomato into the fridge.

high_descs: Go left to the stand with the coffee maker next to the refrigerator.
Take the knife from the stand.
Slice the tomato on the stand.
Go to the right side of the stand.
Put the knife on the stand leaning it on the coffee maker.
Go to the left side of the stand.
Take a slice of tomato from the stand.
Turn around, walk to the front of the stove.
Put the slice of tomato into the pan on the stove.
Take the pan from the stove top.
Turn around, walk to the front of the refrigerator.
Put the pan in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan that has a slice of tomato into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Move to the counter above the dishwasher with the coffee pot on it.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Slice the tomato that is also on the counter.
Move slightly to the right in front of the coffee pot.
Put the knife down on the table.
Move slightly to the left of the counter that has the coffee pot on it.
Pick up a tomato slice off of the counter.
Turn around and move across the room to the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the square pan.
Pick up the pan with the tomato in it.
Turn around and move to the refrigerator.
Place the pan with the tomato on the shelf. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato to place in a pan on the stove to be placed in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the fridge
Pick up the knife beside the tomato on the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Move in front of the coffee maker on the counter
Place the knife with the blade on the front edge of the coffee maker
Move slightly left to in front of the tomato
Take a piece of tomato from beside the left of the coffee maker
Turn around and move towards the stove
Place the slice of tomato in a pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice in it
Turn around and move to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, place the pan and tomato slice inside of it and close the door of the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Putting a slice of tomato in the refrigerator

high_descs: Take a step to the left and face the top of the black cabinet.
Pick up the knife on the black cabinet.
Cut the tomato on the cabinet into slices.
Step to the right and face the top of the cabinet.
Place the knife on the cabinet.
Step to the left to face the tomato on the cabinet.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the cabinet.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the tomato slice on the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice on it on the stove.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Put the pan with the tomato on it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a pan with a tomato slice on it into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around the the counter behind you with the blue coffee pot.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Slice the tomato that is on the left side of the coffee pot.
Move to the other side of this counter.
Put the knife back on the counter top by the coffee pot.
Move to the side of the counter with the sliced tomatoes.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn and cross the room to the stove with the square pan.
Put the tomato in the  pan.
Pick up the pan with the tomato in it.
Turn around and cross the room and go to the refrigerator.
Place the pan on the shelf in the fridge.  Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Preparing food that will be eaten later.
